      "review_summary": "The PR adds `console.warn` diagnostics to five Discord component and exec approval interaction catch blocks while preserving the existing caught-error control flow.\n\nPR surface: Source +10. Total +10 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level, but not as a live setup: current main catches these interaction failures without logging, and the local Discord REST wrapper can throw on failed requests. No contributor-provided real Discord failure log or terminal proof is present.",
